---
title: Harissa Prawns with couscous and Greek style cheese
description: Prawns, peas and juicy sweetcorn form the base of this spicy and slightly sweet stew. A bed of couscous and a final sprinkling of Greek style cheese tie everything together for a nutritious dinner that tastes amazing too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R16_W48_IE_IEQS18291-2_Main_high-dbf31826.jpg
